 rx^{2}+y^{2} > 2brz - bz^{2}, 0<z<2r 
rx^{2}+\sigma y^{2}+\sigma\left(z-2r\right)^{2}=C
=> rx^{2}+y^{2}+(\sigma-1) y^{2}+\sigma\left(z-2r\right)^{2}=C
=> rx^{2}+y^{2}= C -(\sigma-1) y^{2}-\sigma\left(z-2r\right)^{2}
