 2brz - bz^{2} < C -(\sigma-1) y^{2}-\sigma\left(z-2r\right)^{2}, 0<z<2r 
=> bz(2r - z) < C -(\sigma-1) y^{2}-\sigma\left(z-2r\right)^{2}, 0<z<2r 
